    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.wizard.SCUIWizardControllerResponse

  • public class SCUIWizardControllerResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    This calls represents the return type of ISCUIWizardFlowController#processRequest(SCUIWizardMetaData, com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.context.SCUIContext).
